<div id="getting-started" class="docs-section">
  <h2>Getting Started</h2>
  <p>Paperboy is your central hub for submitting, tracking, and managing organizational forms. Here's how to get oriented.</p>

  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Logging In</h4>
    <p>Click <strong>Login with Microsoft</strong> on the home page. You'll be authenticated through your organization's Microsoft Entra ID account.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Sidebar Navigation</h4>
    <p>The left sidebar lists all available forms. Click any form name to open it. On mobile, tap the hamburger menu to reveal the sidebar.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Profile Menu</h4>
    <p>The profile icon in the top-right corner gives you quick access to your <strong>Inbox</strong>, <strong>Submissions</strong>, <strong>Reports</strong>, <strong>Dashboards</strong>, and <strong>Help</strong>. A red badge appears when you have pending inbox items.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Searching for Forms</h4>
    <p>Use the search box at the top of the sidebar to quickly filter and find forms by name.</p>
  </div>
</div>
